org.vadere.util.potential.timecost

Class TimeCost2D1ConfigurationSpace

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.vadere.util.potential.timecost.TimeCost2D1ConfigurationSpace
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITimeCostFunction3D

    public class TimeCost2D1ConfigurationSpace
extends java.lang.Object
implements ITimeCostFunction3D
    Computes a time cost potential field based on obstacles and a rigid body that can be rotated around its center. This creates a 3D time cost field (2 for space, 1 for angle). see Sethian: Level Set Methods and Fast Marching Methods, p. 287ff
